It looks like your current code is using the `key_vault_id` output from the `01_app` module as an input to initialize the module itself. You should instead use the `key_vault_id` output from `01_app` in another piece of infrastructure.

Try doing something like this instead to use `01_app`&#39;s output variable `key_vault_id` in `02_tenant`:

In `02_tenant/main_infra_app.tf`:

    module &quot;kv&quot; {
      source                =   &quot;./01_app&quot;
      key_vault_value_name  =   &quot;somevalue&quot;
    }
    
    data &quot;azurerm_key_vault_secret&quot; &quot;test&quot; {
      name         = &quot;key-vault-name&quot;
      key_vault_id = &quot;${module.kv.key_vault_id}&quot;
    }

So now your code uses `01_app`&#39;s output `key_vault_id` in the `02_tenant` module.

